{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 426768, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "junkseer", "body": "Bolvar, Young Saurfang and their troops are killed by forsaken plague at the gates of Icecrown. After that a 2 separate raids take place, Alliance raid on Undercity to kill \r\nGrand Apothecary Putress responsible for  Bolvar's death and horde raid on Undercity to regain control of the forsaken capital after uprising. This ends in throne room,when after killing Putress, Varian wants to fight Thrall and Sylavanas, but Jaina teleports Alliance force back to Stormwind.", "date": "2008-10-31T18:30:09-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "That would have been an interesting as hell fight.  Damn you and your appeasing ways, Jaina!", "creationdate": "2008-11-07T09:45:35-06:00", "id": 54843, "rating": 19, "commentid": 426768, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "236646", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Like I said before...Alliance got Fear ward and Paladin blessings.", "creationdate": "2008-11-17T16:18:16-06:00", "id": 361423, "rating": 2, "commentid": 426768, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "viva", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "ehm, everyone has fear ward like since ages... paladins too. but the horde got sylvanas singing.", "creationdate": "2008-12-14T16:16:24-06:00", "id": 64702, "rating": 5, "commentid": 426768, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TheMaelstorm", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
